## Development

```bash
# Install with dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Regenerate proto stubs
./scripts/generate_proto.sh

# Run all tests
pytest

# Run unit tests only
pytest tests/unit/

# Run integration tests (spins up an in-process mock server)
pytest tests/integration/

# Type checking
mypy rustycluster/

# Linting
ruff check rustycluster/ tests/
```

